(401,	'Freedom From The Known',	'                                \"Freedom from the Known\" by Jiddu Krishnamurti:\r\n\r\nDive into a transformative exploration of human consciousness with Jiddu Krishnamurti\'s philosophical masterpiece, \"Freedom from the Known.\" In this thought-provoking book, Krishnamurti challenges conventional thinking and invites readers to break free from the constraints of societal conditioning and self-imposed limitations.\r\n\r\nKrishnamurti\'s eloquent prose delves deep into the nature of the mind, the self, and the patterns that govern our lives. He eloquently questions the established norms, belief systems, and dogmas that dictate human behavior, urging readers to engage in self-inquiry and radical self-awareness.\r\n\r\nThrough a series of dialogues and reflections, Krishnamurti encourages us to examine our thoughts, fears, desires, and attachments. He presents a radical approach to inner transformation, advocating for a direct and authentic experience of life beyond the confines of learned knowledge and cultural norms.\r\n\r\n\"Freedom from the Known\" serves as a guide for those seeking to uncover their true selves and embrace the uncharted territory of the present moment. Krishnamurti\'s insights inspire readers to shed their psychological burdens and open themselves to the vast potential of a life lived in freedom, creativity, and awareness.\r\n\r\nThis book is a timeless invitation to embark on a journey of self-discovery, where the familiar is challenged, the mind is liberated, and the possibility of living a life free from the constraints of the known becomes a tangible and inspiring reality. Krishnamurti\'s wisdom continues to resonate with seekers, philosophers, and truth-seekers across generations, offering a profound and enduring guide to inner liberation and profound insight into the nature of existence.                                      ',	202,	'2023-08-30',	302,	'45.67'),
(402,	'Television',	'Introducing the Ultimate Entertainment Companion: Our Cutting-Edge Television Collection!\r\n\r\nStep into a world of immersive visual brilliance with our handpicked selection of state-of-the-art televisions. Elevate your viewing experience to new heights with the latest in display technology, stunning picture quality, and sleek designs that seamlessly blend into any living space. Whether you\'re a movie enthusiast, a sports fanatic, or a gaming aficionado, our televisions deliver an unparalleled level of entertainment that will leave you captivated.\r\n\r\nEnjoy an immersive audio experience with advanced sound technologies that deliver clear dialogue, powerful bass, and nuanced audio effects. Feel like you\'re right in the middle of the action with every sound. Level up your gaming sessions with low input lag and high refresh rates. Our televisions are designed to provide a smooth and responsive gaming experience, making every move and action feel instantaneous.\r\n\r\nConnect all your devices seamlessly with multiple HDMI and USB ports. Whether it\'s a gaming console, soundbar, Blu-ray player, or streaming device, you can effortlessly switch between sources. Experience entertainment redefined with our cutting-edge television collection. Elevate your home viewing setup and enjoy an unparalleled entertainment journey that will keep you coming back for more. Shop now and bring the cinema, the stadium, and the gaming world right into your living room!                ',	201,	'2023-08-31',	302,	'77.43'),
(403,	'Refrigerators',	'Introducing the Ultimate Refrigerator Collection for Modern Homes!\r\n\r\nWelcome to our state-of-the-art refrigerator ecommerce store, where innovation meets style to transform your kitchen into a hub of convenience and elegance. Discover a curated selection of top-tier refrigerators designed to cater to your diverse needs while complementing your contemporary lifestyle.\r\nOur refrigerators aren\'t just appliances; they\'re the embodiment of sophistication. With sleek lines, premium finishes, and thoughtfully crafted details, they seamlessly blend with your kitchen decor, elevating its aesthetic appeal. But it\'s not just about looks – these refrigerators are engineered for efficiency and convenience. From adjustable shelving to smart storage compartments, every element is designed to enhance usability and maximize space.\r\n\r\nBid farewell to food spoilage worries! Our refrigerators boast cutting-edge cooling technologies that ensure optimal preservation of your groceries. Advanced temperature control systems maintain consistent coldness, while humidity regulation keeps fruits and vegetables fresher for longer. Say hello to extended food shelf life and reduced wastage. Welcome to the future of kitchen appliances. Many of our refrigerators are equipped with smart features that bring convenience to your fingertips. Control temperature settings remotely, receive alerts for open doors, and even create shopping lists based on your inventory. With seamless integration into your smart home ecosystem, managing your fridge has never been this effortless.\r\n\r\nWe understand that every household has unique needs. That\'s why we offer a diverse range of refrigerator styles and sizes to cater to various preferences. Whether you\'re a busy professional, a gourmet chef, or a family with active kids, you\'ll find the perfect refrigerator that suits your lifestyle and dietary requirements. Upgrade your kitchen with a refrigerator that\'s more than just an appliance – it\'s a statement of your refined taste and a reflection of your commitment to quality. Explore our collection today and experience the future of refrigeration!                ',	201,	'2023-08-30',	302,	'23.77'),
(404,	'Zero To One',	'In \"Zero to One,\" legendary entrepreneur and investor Peter Thiel takes you on a transformative journey from zero to the realm of revolutionary innovation – from creating something entirely new (\"Zero to One\") rather than merely copying what already exists (\"One to N\"). Drawing from his experiences co-founding PayPal and investing in companies like Facebook, Thiel shares his invaluable insights on how to build a successful startup that goes beyond incremental improvements to usher in a new era of progress.\r\n\r\n\"Zero to One\" isn\'t just another business book; it\'s a manifesto for those who aspire to shape the future. Whether you\'re a seasoned entrepreneur or just starting your journey, this book is your compass, guiding you through the uncharted territory of innovation. Thiel\'s thought-provoking insights and contrarian views will challenge your assumptions and inspire you to create something extraordinary. Join the ranks of forward-thinkers who have embraced the wisdom of \"Zero to One.\" Experience the power of innovation and learn how to create and capture value in ways that defy convention. Get your copy today and embark on a transformative adventure that will change the way you view business, innovation, and the world itself.                ',	202,	'2023-08-28',	302,	'20.23'),
(405,	'Jeans Pant\'s',	'Our jeans are more than just pants; they\'re a testament to quality craftsmanship. Each pair is meticulously designed and crafted using premium denim that offers durability and comfort, ensuring your investment lasts through countless wears and washes. Reinforced stitching and attention to detail make these jeans stand the test of time. We understand that diversity is key when it comes to fashion. That\'s why our collection offers a variety of fits, from the classic slim fit that hugs your curves to the relaxed fit that provides ease of movement. Embrace your individuality and find the perfect pair that complements your body type and style.\r\n\r\nA well-fitting pair of jeans is the ultimate wardrobe staple, effortlessly transitioning from day to night and from casual to semi-formal settings. Dress them up with a crisp shirt and blazer or go casual with a graphic tee – the possibilities are endless. Our jeans are designed to be the canvas upon which you can create your signature style. Step into the world of fashion-forward denim that caters to your lifestyle. Our jeans pants aren\'t just an article of clothing; they\'re an expression of your personality and a reflection of your taste. Explore our collection today and find the pair that resonates with you. Elevate your style with jeans that don\'t just fit your body – they fit your life.              ',	205,	'2023-08-27',	302,	'454.6'),
(406,	'Deodrants',	'Say goodbye to worries about unwanted body odor. Our deodorants are formulated with advanced technology that neutralizes odor-causing bacteria, providing you with long-lasting freshness that stands up to the rigors of your active lifestyle. Feel confident and comfortable, even during the most demanding moments.\r\nWe believe that effective deodorants shouldn\'t compromise your skin\'s health. That\'s why our collection features options that are dermatologist-tested and formulated with skin-friendly ingredients. Experience the gentle touch of our deodorants while they work hard to keep you smelling great.\r\n\r\nChoosing a deodorant is about more than just odor protection – it\'s a chance to express your personality. Our range includes an array of captivating scents, from invigorating citrus bursts to sophisticated woody notes. Whether you\'re looking for an everyday fresh scent or a special fragrance for an occasion, we have the perfect match for you. Life is full of unexpected moments, and we\'ve got you covered. Our travel-sized deodorants are perfect companions for your gym bag, office drawer, or weekend getaway. Stay fresh wherever you are, without compromising on your comfort or confidence.\r\n\r\nYour journey to all-day freshness starts here. Explore our diverse deodorants collection and discover the scent that resonates with your personality and lifestyle. Embrace confidence, embrace comfort – choose the deodorant that\'s tailored to you.               ',	204,	'2023-08-30',	302,	'55.7'),
(407,	'Cars',	'Discover a world of automotive excellence as you step into our virtual showroom. With a curated selection of the finest cars, we\'re here to help you find your dream ride, whether you\'re seeking luxury, performance, or everyday practicality. Experience the thrill of browsing through a diverse range of top-notch vehicles, all from the comfort of your own home.  \r\n\r\nFor those who demand the utmost in opulence and refinement, our luxury car collection will captivate your senses. Immerse yourself in the finest materials, cutting-edge technology, and exquisite craftsmanship that define these vehicles. Elevate your driving experience to an entirely new level of sophistication. For the adrenaline enthusiast, our range of high-performance cars will set your heart racing. Experience the sheer power, precision engineering, and exhilarating driving dynamics that these vehicles offer. From nimble roadsters to powerful muscle cars, get ready to feel the road like never before.\r\n\r\nQuality knows no age, and our pre-owned cars collection proves just that. Explore a range of meticulously maintained, certified pre-owned vehicles that offer incredible value without compromising on quality. Get behind the wheel of a premium car at an exceptional price point. Our team of automotive experts is dedicated to providing you with a personalized and seamless shopping experience. Whether you\'re seeking advice on choosing the perfect model, arranging financing options, or exploring vehicle features, we\'re here to guide you every step of the way.              ',	208,	'2023-08-28',	302,	'32.76'),
(408,	'Baby Doll',	'Our baby doll collection features an exquisite array of lifelike creations that closely mimic the beauty of real infants. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, these dolls boast delicate features, soft skin-like textures, and captivating eyes that mirror the innocence of infancy. Each baby doll in our collection is a work of art. From the hand-painted features to the intricate stitching of clothing, our artisans pour their expertise into every detail, ensuring that every doll is a testament to their skill and dedication.\r\n\r\nA baby doll from our collection isn\'t just a gift; it\'s a timeless treasure that can be passed down through generations. Whether it\'s a cherished heirloom or a companion for a young child, our dolls have the power to create lasting memories. Explore our enchanting selection of lifelike baby dolls and embark on a journey of wonder and imagination. These dolls transcend the boundaries of play, inviting you to create magical moments and heartfelt connections that will be cherished forever. Welcome to a world where innocence, beauty, and joy come to life – welcome to our baby doll ecommerce paradise.\r\n\r\nWe prioritize the safety and happiness of our customers, especially the little ones. Our baby dolls are crafted from high-quality materials that are gentle on young hands, and they undergo rigorous safety testing to ensure they meet the highest standards.           ',	207,	'2023-09-08',	302,	'90.65'),
(409,	'Football',	'Our collection boasts a comprehensive range of football essentials, from top-tier footballs and jerseys to protective gear and accessories. Each product is carefully selected to ensure superior quality, durability, and performance, helping you elevate your game to new heights. Support your favorite team with pride by exploring our selection of football jerseys and fan merchandise. From international powerhouses to local clubs, we have a variety of jerseys that allow you to showcase your allegiance on and off the field.\r\n\r\nFootball is for everyone, and our collection reflects that. From kids\' sizes to adult gear, we cater to players of all ages and skill levels. Whether you\'re nurturing a future star or reliving your own playing days, we have the right gear for you. We prioritize authenticity and quality in every product we offer. Our footballs are meticulously designed to meet official standards, ensuring optimal performance on the field. The apparel and gear we carry are sourced from reputable brands known for their commitment to excellence.\r\n\r\nStep onto the pitch with confidence and style by exploring our extensive football collection. From playing gear to fan merchandise, we\'re here to fuel your passion and celebrate the excitement of football. Join us in embracing the beautiful game and discover a world of possibilities on and off the field. Step onto the pitch with confidence and style by exploring our extensive football collection. From playing gear to fan merchandise, we\'re here to fuel your passion and celebrate the excitement of football. Join us in embracing the beautiful game and discover a world of possibilities on and off the field.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n                ',	206,	'2023-08-30',	302,	'24.93'),
(410,	'Eye Glasses',	'Our eyeglasses collection showcases an array of frames that cater to every style preference and face shape. From sleek and minimalistic designs to bold and statement-making choices, you\'ll find frames that not only enhance your vision but also elevate your overall look. Seeing is believing, and our commitment to optical excellence ensures that you\'ll experience unmatched clarity. Our lenses are crafted using the latest lens technology, offering crisp vision, reduced glare, and enhanced color perception. Say goodbye to eyestrain and hello to uncompromised visual comfort.\r\n\r\nFor those who need corrective lenses, we offer a seamless process to incorporate your prescription into the eyeglasses of your choice. Our precise lens customization ensures that your eyeglasses not only look stylish but also cater to your unique vision needs. Embrace style, comfort, and exceptional vision by exploring our eyeglasses collection. From prescription glasses to fashion-forward frames, we\'re dedicated to helping you see and be seen in the best possible light. Step into a world where clarity meets creativity and discover the eyeglasses that perfectly frame your unique perspective.                ',	203,	'2023-08-27',	302,	'24.67'),
(411,	'Guitars',	'                                                Our guitars are more than just instruments; they\'re works of art. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, each guitar showcases exceptional craftsmanship that results in impeccable sound, impeccable playability, and exquisite aesthetics. Experience the beauty of sound as you strum, pick, and pluck your way to creating captivating melodies. Our guitars offer a diverse range of tones, from rich and warm acoustic notes to electrifying riffs that will make your audience groove.\r\n\r\nYour guitar is an extension of your creativity and personality. Our collection features a wide array of designs, finishes, and shapes, allowing you to find the guitar that resonates with your unique style. Our team of guitar enthusiasts and experts is here to guide you through the selection process. From choosing the right type of guitar to exploring the perfect accessories, we\'re committed to helping you make an informed and inspired choice. We prioritize quality in every instrument we offer. Our guitars come from reputable brands known for their commitment to excellence, ensuring that you receive an instrument that is built to last and perform exceptionally.\r\n\r\nYour quest for the perfect guitar ends here. Explore our collection and embark on a musical journey that will enrich your life and empower your artistic endeavors. From the first note to the final crescendo, discover the magic of music with our exceptional guitars.                                                                ',	209,	'2023-08-30',	301,	'67.23'),
(412,	'Sneakers',	'Our sneaker collection is a showcase of the latest trends and timeless classics, offering you a wide variety of styles to suit your personal aesthetic. From sleek and minimalistic designs to vibrant and bold statements, we have sneakers that cater to every taste and preference. Your feet deserve the best, and our sneakers deliver. Crafted with cutting-edge comfort technology, each pair ensures that every step you take is a cushioned and supported experience. Walk, run, and explore without compromising on comfort.\r\n\r\nWe prioritize quality and durability in every sneaker we offer. Our collection features sneakers from renowned brands known for their craftsmanship, ensuring that you receive footwear that is built to last.\r\nSneakers are a canvas for self-expression, and our collection allows you to showcase your individuality. Choose from a spectrum of colors, patterns, and materials to find the pair that resonates with your style and personality. Navigating our sneaker collection is a breeze, and with our detailed product descriptions and images, you can confidently make your selection. Our customer support team is also here to address any queries and assist you throughout your shopping journey.                ',	205,	'2023-08-29',	301,	'13.98'),
(413,	'Table Tennis',	'Our table tennis collection showcases a range of paddles, balls, and accessories that are designed to enhance your playing experience. From entry-level options for beginners to professional-grade equipment for serious competitors, we have the tools you need to excel. Table tennis is all about finesse, and our equipment reflects that ethos. Our paddles are expertly crafted with attention to detail, using cutting-edge materials that provide the perfect blend of control, spin, and power.\r\n\r\nTable tennis is more than just paddles and balls. Our collection also includes nets, table covers, training aids, and more, all designed to enhance your practice sessions and ensure you\'re always ready for a match. For those aiming for greatness, our selection includes professional-grade equipment endorsed by champions and experts in the sport. Elevate your game with gear that has been crafted to meet the demands of competitive play.\r\n\r\nNavigating our table tennis collection is as smooth as executing a perfect serve. Detailed product descriptions, customer reviews, and expert recommendations ensure you\'re making informed choices. Our customer support team is also here to assist you in finding the right equipment for your needs. From casual recreation to serious competition, our table tennis equipment is your gateway to hours of thrilling gameplay. Experience the thrill of fast-paced rallies, masterful spins, and strategic plays with our exceptional collection. Step onto the table with confidence and embrace the world of table tennis excellence.                ',	206,	'2023-08-30',	301,	'25.76'),
(414,	'Jwellery',	'Our jewelry collection is a celebration of enduring elegance that transcends trends and seasons. From delicate necklaces to statement-making bracelets, each piece is meticulously crafted to capture the essence of sophistication and grace. Discover jewelry that\'s not just accessories, but masterpieces. Our pieces are brought to life by skilled artisans who combine age-old techniques with modern creativity, resulting in jewelry that\'s as unique as you are.\r\n\r\nJewelry is a canvas for self-expression, and our collection allows you to showcase your individuality. Choose from a range of styles – from vintage-inspired classics to contemporary designs – that resonate with your personality and tastes. Whether you\'re marking a special milestone, expressing your love, or simply treating yourself, our jewelry collection offers pieces that are suited for a variety of occasions. Find the perfect accessory to complement your outfit or celebrate life\'s cherished moments.\r\n\r\nOur jewelry isn\'t just for personal adornment; it\'s also a heartfelt gift that carries emotions and memories. Whether it\'s a symbol of love, friendship, or appreciation, our pieces are destined to make the recipient feel truly cherished.                ',	203,	'2023-08-31',	301,	'25.76'),
(415,	'Face Wash',	'Our face wash collection is designed to transform your skincare routine into a spa-like experience. With gentle yet effective formulations, each face wash removes impurities, excess oil, and makeup without stripping your skin of its natural moisture. We understand that every skin type is unique. Whether you have oily, dry, sensitive, or combination skin, our range includes face wash options tailored to your specific needs. Achieve balance and harmony in your skincare routine.\r\n\r\nOur collection goes beyond cleansing – it addresses common skin concerns such as acne, blemishes, aging, and uneven tone. Explore specialized face wash options that offer targeted solutions for achieving your desired complexion. A well-rounded skincare routine begins with the right cleanser. Our face wash products set the stage for the rest of your routine, ensuring that your serums, moisturizers, and treatments can work effectively to deliver visible results.                ',	204,	'2023-08-29',	301,	'33.93'),
(416,	'Bullet Bike',	'Our bullet bikes capture the essence of the open road with their iconic design that pays homage to the golden era of motorcycles. The vintage-inspired aesthetics are coupled with modern engineering to create a harmonious blend of nostalgia and innovation. Prepare to be captivated by the exhilarating power and performance of our bullet bikes. Equipped with advanced engines and precision engineering, these bikes deliver unmatched acceleration, speed, and handling that redefines your riding experience.\r\n\r\nWhile performance is paramount, comfort is equally essential. Our bullet bikes are designed with ergonomic features that ensure a comfortable riding position, even during long journeys. Enjoy every ride without compromising on comfort. Whether you\'re embarking on a solo journey or riding with friends, our bullet bikes are your trusted companions for exploring new horizons. Experience the freedom of the open road as you create unforgettable memories on two wheels.\r\n\r\nEmbark on a journey that promises excitement, freedom, and a connection to the road like never before. Explore our bullet bikes collection and choose the ride that resonates with your spirit of adventure. Get ready to experience the exhilaration of the open road on a bike that\'s built to ignite your passion for riding.                ',	208,	'2023-08-31',	301,	'1246.95'),
(417,	'Book Shelf',	'Our bookshelf collection offers a range of designs that cater to diverse tastes and interior styles. From sleek modern lines to rustic charm, our bookshelves are not only storage solutions but also elegant pieces of furniture that enhance the beauty of your space. We believe that furniture should stand the test of time. Our bookshelves are crafted with meticulous attention to detail, using high-quality materials that ensure durability and longevity. Each piece is a testament to expert craftsmanship.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re furnishing a cozy reading nook or revamping your entire living area, our bookshelves come in various sizes and configurations to suit your needs. Choose from wall-mounted shelves, ladder-style bookcases, corner units, and more. Our bookshelves aren\'t just aesthetic additions to your space; they\'re also functional storage solutions that help you keep your belongings organized. From novels and magazines to electronics and keepsakes, our shelves offer ample room to declutter your living area.                ',	209,	'2023-08-27',	301,	'345.99'),
(418,	'Remote Control Car',	'Our remote control cars are more than just toys; they\'re a gateway to exhilarating adventures. Watch as your child\'s eyes light up with excitement while they control the speed, maneuver through obstacles, and create their very own race courses. Designed with young drivers in mind, our remote control cars feature intuitive controls that are simple to master. Let your child experience the joy of navigating their car with ease, honing their coordination skills along the way.\r\n\r\nFrom indoor races to outdoor escapades, our remote control cars are versatile companions for your child\'s playtime. Spark their imagination as they create thrilling stories and scenarios while zooming around. Remote control cars aren\'t just about speed; they encourage imaginative play and exploration. Watch as your child invents their own mini-adventures, setting the stage for hours of creative fun. Whether it\'s a birthday, holiday, or simply a surprise gift, our remote control cars are guaranteed to put a smile on your child\'s face. Give them the gift of excitement, exploration, and endless playtime memories.                ',	207,	'2023-08-29',	301,	'345.77')
